    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >史上最强大的骑士兼伟大城市克莱西亚的守护者Lionstone爵士自上次前去执行任务以后，就再也没有归来。作为深受Lionstone爵士信任的见习骑士，你需要拿起他留下的传奇盾牌，成为人们所期待的英雄。此外，王国周围危机四伏，你需要在危险真正袭来之前找到Lionstone。探索克莱西亚的众多地区和各种秘密，抵御强盗和怪物，唤醒盾牌无可比拟的神力，揭开王国过往辉煌的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>万般英雄，皆始于无名之辈</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演一名正在接受训练的见习骑士，你的忠诚和决心将带你踏上一场寻找骑士长的伟大冒险。你的手中只有一面盾牌，你需要借助自己的训练所得，并不断升级各种能力，在冒险途中排除万难，同时帮助平民，证明你配得上“骑士”之名。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471650/extras/011bfd8d7be6e077abc63d3fbb094371.poster.avif?t=1772018265\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471650/extras/011bfd8d7be6e077abc63d3fbb094371.webm?t=1772018265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471650/extras/011bfd8d7be6e077abc63d3fbb094371.mp4?t=1772018265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>良好的防御就是最好的进攻</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >留给你的只有Lionstone爵士的盾牌，其中包含着名为卡里瑞姆的神秘元素。作为见习骑士，你需要驾驭盾牌的力量，成为下一个传奇英雄。利用盾牌的天然防御能力来格挡、招架，让敌人露出破绽，然后利用蓄力攻击和连击来消灭敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471650/extras/209d2e3ce3f8c67bd89538ff24f0e09d.poster.avif?t=1772018265\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471650/extras/209d2e3ce3f8c67bd89538ff24f0e09d.webm?t=1772018265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471650/extras/209d2e3ce3f8c67bd89538ff24f0e09d.mp4?t=1772018265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>踏上冒险之路</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用盾牌的力量，在克莱西亚的多个地区开始你的冒险！在各个地区之间来回穿梭，获得宝贵的赞誉，并将其用于升级能力。你也可以使用盾牌的各种移动能力来快速前行，虽然这对于传奇盾牌来说可能有点大材小用，但请放心，没有人会阻止你在这片土地上穿行！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471650/extras/aa6c8d52951792a70a33f2e6e93f81a9.poster.avif?t=1772018265\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471650/extras/aa6c8d52951792a70a33f2e6e93f81a9.webm?t=1772018265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471650/extras/aa6c8d52951792a70a33f2e6e93f81a9.mp4?t=1772018265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
